import React, { useState } from 'react'; import Axios from 'axios'; function ApplicantForm() { const url="http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/apply/"; const [data,setData]=useState({ Name:"", FName:"Sar", Gender:"Male", DOB:"2002-04-04", Age:"18", Category:"ABC", Ward:"EKV", SubDistrict:"Erode", District:"Erode", State:"Tamilnadu", Pincode:"123456", Mobile:"9087654321", AadharNo:"123456789012", Disablity:"No", DisabilityType:"None", BPL_Family_ID:"ded", BankDetails:"Nothin", IGNOAPS:"Yes", IGNWPS:"Yes", IGNDPS:"Yes", NFBS:"Yes" }) function submit(e) { e.preventDefault(); Axios.post(url,{ Name:data.Name, FName:data.FName, Gender:data.Gender, DOB:data.DOB, Age:data.Age, Category:data.Category, Ward:data.Ward, SubDistrict:data.SubDistrict, District:data.District, State:data.State, Pincode:data.Pincode, Mobile:data.Mobile, AadharNo:data.AadharNo, Disablity:data.Disablity, DisabilityType:data.DisabilityType, BPL_Family_ID:data.BPL_Family_ID, BankDetails:data.BankDetails, IGNOAPS:data.IGNOAPS, IGNWPS:data.IGNWPS, IGNDPS:data.IGNDPS, NFBS:data.NFBS }).then(res=>{ console.log(res.data); }) } function handle(e) { const newdata=(...data)=> newdata[e.target.id]=e.target.value setData(newdata) console.log(newdata) } return(
submit(e)}> handle(e)} id="Name" value={data.Name} placeholder='Name' type="text"> handle(e)} id="Fname" value={data.FName} placeholder='Fname' type='text'> handle(e)} id="Gender" value={data.Gender} placeholder='Gender' type='text'> handle(e)} id="DOB'" value={data.value} placeholder='DOB' type='text'> handle(e)} id="Age" value={data.value} placeholder='Age' type='number'> handle(e)} id="Category" value={data.value} placeholder='Category' type='text'> handle(e)} id="Ward" value={data.value} placeholder='Ward' type='text'> handle(e)} id="SubDistrict" value={data.value} placeholder='SubDistrict' type='text'> handle(e)} id="District" value={data.value} placeholder='District' type='text'> handle(e)} id="State" value={data.value} placeholder='State' type='text'> handle(e)} id="Pincode" value={data.value} placeholder='Pincode' type='number'> handle(e)} id="Mobile" value={data.value} placeholder='Mobile' type='number'> handle(e)} id="AadharNo" value={data.value} placeholder='AadharNo' type='number'> handle(e)} id="Disability" value={data.value} placeholder='Disability' type='text'> handle(e)} id="DisabilityType" value={data.value} placeholder='DisabilityType' type='text'> handle(e)} id="BPL_Family_ID" value={data.value} placeholder='BPL_Family_ID' type='text'> handle(e)} id="BankDetails" value={data.value} placeholder='BankDetails' type='text'> handle(e)} id="IGNOAPS" value={data.value} placeholder='IGNOAPS' type='text'> handle(e)} id="IGNWPS" value={data.value} placeholder='IGNWPS' type='text'> handle(e)} id="IGNDPS" value={data.value} placeholder='IGNDPS' type='text'> handle(e)} id="NFBS" value={data.value} placeholder='NFBS' type='text'>
); } export default ApplicantForm;
